% query population and area database to find countries of approximately equal population density. 
query_pop([C1,D1,C2,D2]) :-
 density(C1,D1),
 density(C2,D2),
 D1 > D2,
 T1 is 20*D1,
 T2 is 21*D2,
 T1 < T2.
density(C,D) :-
 pop(C,P),
 area(C,A),
 D is (P*100)//A.
